msgctxt "Npc_Musician_AoC_HeroGoronRelief_201"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I can imagine it vividly...the Champion's\n"
"vigilance from 100 years ago."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Npc_Musician_AoC_HeroGoronRelief_202"
msgid ""
"<1.so>My teacher always advised that, to write\n"
"good songs, one must travel the world\n"
"and meet lots of people."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
#. 6: set_colour (blue)
#. 7: reset_colour
msgctxt "Npc_Musician_AoC_HeroGoronRelief_203"
msgid ""
"<1.so>That is why I spend my days afoot,\n"
"talking to anyone who will listen.\n"
"\n"
"I was lucky enough to meet with <2.se_co>Yunobo<3.re_co>\n"
"and <4.se_co>Bludo<5.re_co> in <6.se_co>Goron City<7.re_co>, both of whom"
"\n"
"knew much about the Goron Champion.\n"
"They regaled me with some rather\n"
"interesting stories!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "Npc_Musician_AoC_HeroGoronRelief_204"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm certain the stories they shared will\n"
"help greatly in my efforts to accurately\n"
"write the song's <2.se_co>key verses<3.re_co>."
msgstr ""

